    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i have seen the doctors. a support group. i’ve done it all. they just keep saying \"manage it\" or \"try this new pill\" but nothing works. it's just a cycle of more pain and more pills. it feels like a cruel joke. there's no relief, just a different kind of misery. honestly, i just look at the end of things and think... wouldn't it just be a mercy if it finally stopped? if i could just have some peace and stillness?",
